title: 'Poor Quality Adhesive Tape'
body: The media could not be loaded. Tape is flimsy & very thin and it's breaking in between while taking out for use. It is not serving the purpose for which I had bought. It is marked non returnable. As a customer, I will know it's quality (good or bad) only after getting and trying it.

body: 'I have used these tapes to make ten boxes for packing books and the adhesion is really good. Worth buying.'
